South Africa’s Alexkor Gem Mine Closed Due to Safety, Business Report Says

-- B y   A n t o n y   S g u a z z i n
-- 
2011-06-08T04:31:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-08/south-africa-s-alexkor-gem-mine-closed-on-safety-business-report-says.html
South Africa ’s state-owned Alexkor
diamond mine has been closed by health and safety inspectors
because earthmoving equipment and vehicles at the operation were
found to be unsafe, Johannesburg’s Business Report said, without
saying where it got the information.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
